companyInfo.introduction: CTCP Vincom Retail tin thn l Cng ty TNHH Vincom Retail, c thnh lp vo nm 2012 v l thnh vin ca Tp on Vingroup (VIC). Vi s mnh pht trin v vn hnh h thng trung tm thng mi Vincom, VRE  t c v th ng ch  trong ngnh bn l. Cng ty chuyn hot ng trong vic cho thu cc trung tm thng mi bn l v cung cp cc dch v lin quan, cng vi vic u t v kinh doanh bt ng sn. VRE s hu 80 trung tm thng mi, vi din tch sn bn l trn 1.7 triu m2, ta lc ti 43 tnh thnh ph trn ton quc. M hnh sn phm ca cng ty bao gm Vincom Center, Vincom Mega Mall, Vincom Plaza v Vincom+.
